column9: Peter was not very well during the evening. His mother put him to bed, and made some chamomile tea: One table-spoonful to be taken at bedtime

The patient P. Rabbit (first name Peter) was admitted to our hospital on 14-02-2023 with symptoms of chamomile tea poisoning. His mother Mrs. Rabbit-Konijn, admitted administrating too much tea. Patient name: RABBIT,P.
